            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>meat-free mince</strong>,<strong> chopped mint</strong>,<strong> ground cumin </strong>and<strong> half</strong> of the <strong>chopped chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a bowl</p><p>Using clean hands, give everything a very good mix up until fully combined</p><p>Divide the <strong>meat-free</strong> <strong>mince mixture</strong> into 10<span class=\"text-danger\"> [20]</span> and roll into meatballs</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
