    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>meat-free mince meatball masala </strong>over the <strong>brown rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> remaining chopped chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
